# ------------------------------------

Python Character Set

• Letters = A to Z, a to z
• Digits = 0 to 9
• Special Symbols = + - * / etc.
• Whitespaces = Blank Space, tab, carriage return, newline, formfeed
• Other characters = Python can process all ASCIl and Unicode characters as part of data or literals


